      "content": "\"let go and stop fighting against the silence\"... that's a pretty heavy thing to say. are you saying that fighting to stay here is actually irrational? like, if the outcome is always going to be nothingness, why is it considered \"courageous\" to struggle against it instead of just accepting the end?",
